00:24:22,600 --> 00:24:24,500
Look, I'll show you something...

295
00:24:24,600 --> 00:24:28,800
She was assigned to sort
and file the individual trace elements...

296
00:24:28,900 --> 00:24:30,800
Hair, fiber mostly...

297
00:24:32,600 --> 00:24:35,600
You know, from each of the 14 scenes.

298
00:24:37,700 --> 00:24:39,000
