you are on your own.

315
00:25:47,400 --> 00:25:49,200
- So it's all bullshit.
- I dunno.

316
00:25:49,200 --> 00:25:51,400
I thought the mayor
gave a very nice speech.

317
00:25:51,400 --> 00:25:55,100
