00:26:43,300 --> 00:26:45,200
I'm responsible.

325
00:26:47,700 --> 00:26:50,600
A week or so back,
I made a move on Omar, with Joe's approval.

326
00:26:50,600 --> 00:26:54,100
The faggot ain't had heart enough to come
at me, so he come at those close to me.

327
00:26:54,100 --> 00:26:56,500
Now I'm doublin' the bounty...

328
00:26:56,500 --> 00:27:00,300
Hundred large for a whiff of that dicksuck.

329
00:27:00,400 --> 00:27:02,500
Two hundred fifty for his head.

330
00:27:02,500 --> 00:27:05,700
- What about the connect?
- I got that covered.

331
00:27:05,700 --> 00:27:09,700
