myself to conduct this meet.

332
00:27:11,200 --> 00:27:14,500
Slim, I want you take over
Hungry Man's slice of the cake.

333
00:27:15,200 --> 00:27:19,500
Meanin' no disrespect,
but I ain't cut out to be no CEO.

334
00:27:24,300 --> 00:27:27,900
