On the Eastside, Cheese.

340
00:27:47,400 --> 00:27:49,400
One more thing.

341
00:27:49,400 --> 00:27:51,700
Price of the brick going up.

342
00:27:51,800 --> 00:27:53,400
Thirty more.

343
00:27:55,900 --> 00:27:57,800
