to report from the street?

357
00:29:01,200 --> 00:29:04,100
No, not at all.
I mean, this is what we do.

358
00:29:04,100 --> 00:29:07,500
As a reporter, you expect to be
in harm's way at some points.

359
00:29:07,600 --> 00:29:10,500
- It's what we do.
