360
00:29:10,500 --> 00:29:15,000
But very rarely does a reporter end up
being in the middle of a story -

361
00:29:15,100 --> 00:29:16,800
an ongoing story -

362
00:29:16,900 --> 00:29:22,700
about a murderer who is still at large
and posing a severe and deadly risk to the...

363
00:29:23,800 --> 00:29:26,200
You shoulda heard Phelan this morning.

364
00:29:26,300 --> 00:29:30,100
Too scared to tap the newspaper phones
they might shit on him for it.

365
00:29:31,200 --> 00:29:32,900
Fuckin' hack judge.

