00:31:19,600 --> 00:31:21,600
Didn't think so.

393
00:31:31,300 --> 00:31:33,100
What now?

394
00:31:33,900 --> 00:31:36,200
There's more than one way to skin a case.

395
00:31:48,200 --> 00:31:50,200
Already ran them for priors, right?

396
00:31:50,200 --> 00:31:53,300
Priors, yeah. But I'm gonna run
every name you guys developed

397
00:31:53,400 --> 00:31:54,900
